1
00:00:01,160 --> 00:00:06,110
Hey, guys. Do you feel
like we're being watched?

2
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:07,410
[ALL]
Huh?

3
00:00:09,530 --> 00:00:14,530
♪

4
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,160
[LIUYUE JIANG]
"Routine Maintenance

5
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:58,780
of a Spiritual Sword.
Season Two."

6
00:01:58,860 --> 00:02:00,160
[WANG ZUKANG]
Listen up.

7
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,820
The more we utilize our
swords in our daily lives,

8
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:04,990
the more problems they develop.

9
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:14,780
[WANG ZUKANG]
For instance, they become blunt,

10
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:16,990
[gasps]

11
00:02:17,070 --> 00:02:18,860
[WANG ZUKANG]
or run slower than usual.

12
00:02:18,950 --> 00:02:20,950
Not good.

13
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:23,910
This means that your swords
are unhappy, period.

14
00:02:23,990 --> 00:02:26,360
[AUDIENCE]
Oh!

15
00:02:26,450 --> 00:02:29,990
[WANG ZUKANG] The metal gets
dull after repeated impacts,

16
00:02:30,070 --> 00:02:32,950
or when it's used
inappropriately.

17
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:35,990
An unhealthy diet can have
especially negative effects.

18
00:02:36,070 --> 00:02:38,410
[WANG ZUKANG sighs] If you're
careless, you can cause

19
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:40,990
irreversible damage to
the sword and its spirit.

20
00:02:41,070 --> 00:02:43,070
[LIUYUE JIANG] Whatever shall
we do, Professor Zukang?

21
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:45,780
Read my book!
<i>Spiritual Swords and Me</i> .

22
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:47,200
Available now!

23
00:02:49,610 --> 00:02:52,030
[JINGKE SWORD] Master, you know
I haven't had any maintenance

24
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:53,570
since I was forged.

25
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:54,450
[WANG LING]
Hm.

26
00:02:54,530 --> 00:02:56,030
[WANG ZUKANG]
Be ready.

27
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:58,490
This year's advanced spiritual
sword classes start next week.

28
00:02:58,570 --> 00:02:59,950
Make sure to have
your swords ready

29
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:02,110
before those lessons begin.

30
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,450
[GUO HAO]
Hey, Sun Rong.

31
00:03:07,530 --> 00:03:09,570
Did you ever get
your sword fixed?

32
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:12,490
Well, we finished
reforging the body,

33
00:03:12,570 --> 00:03:14,490
but the spirit still needs time.

34
00:03:14,570 --> 00:03:16,740
[SUN RONG chuckles]
It's fine.

35
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:19,660
So, you guys taking good
care of your swords?

36
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:22,990
[CHEN CHAO chuckles] Your boy
bought himself a maintenance kit

37
00:03:23,070 --> 00:03:24,360
from the internet.

38
00:03:24,450 --> 00:03:26,820
[SUN RONG] But the only tool
kits you can find online

39
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:29,360
are for Class C
swords and below.

40
00:03:29,450 --> 00:03:32,200
Like Zukang said,
medium or large swords

41
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,320
have to be taken
to a Four-S shop.

42
00:03:34,410 --> 00:03:38,860
Mine is a Class D, and it
needs service regularly.

43
00:03:38,950 --> 00:03:40,110
Your sword is extra-large,

44
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,280
there's no way to
do that at home.

45
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:44,860
She's not wrong. Mine got rusty.

46
00:03:44,950 --> 00:03:46,030
It could use some love.

47
00:03:46,110 --> 00:03:48,200
Dude, you should really
take care of that.

48
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:51,570
And whaddaya know? My kit's
perfect for small swords

49
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:54,780
like yours, so let me
help ya out!

50
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:58,320
There's a shop near my house.
Appreciate the offer, though!

51
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:02,240
I can even get 20% off!

52
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:04,780
[SUN RONG]
Oh, you mean this shop?

53
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:07,070
You're looking at a VIP member!

54
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,700
Hey, Wang Ling.

55
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:12,820
If you're not too busy, would
you wanna hang out with us?

56
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:16,280
Oh, I forgot to ask.
How's your sword?

57
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,410
[WOMEN giggling]

58
00:04:18,490 --> 00:04:20,570
[NARRATOR]
Wang Ling's sword, Jing Ke,

59
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:22,740
is technically a mature spirit.

60
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:26,200
Which means he gets his
maintenance without supervision.

61
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,910
[CHEN CHAO] Whoa, look at it!
It's beautiful!

62
00:04:31,990 --> 00:04:34,320
Are all Four-S shops like this?

63
00:04:34,410 --> 00:04:37,070
No, this is their
flagship store.

64
00:04:38,490 --> 00:04:42,070
[CHEN CHAO, GUO HAO gasp]

65
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,820
[GUO HAO]
Whoa! Check it out!

66
00:04:43,910 --> 00:04:45,610
The Legendary Fire's Joy,

67
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:48,360
I read about it in Popular
Blades magazine!

68
00:04:48,450 --> 00:04:49,910
--[SUN RONG gasps]
--[CHEN CHAO] No way!

69
00:04:49,990 --> 00:04:52,240
Is anyone strong enough
to use this thing?

70
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:54,160
[XIAOYU LIN] Ever heard
of the ancient Juque?

71
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,030
It's the pride of our shop.

72
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:56,990
[ALL]
Lin Xiaoyu!

73
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:58,320
[XIAOYU LIN giggles]

74
00:05:00,490 --> 00:05:01,360
[XIAOYU LIN grunts]

75
00:05:01,450 --> 00:05:02,820
[SUN RONG, GUO HAO gasp]

76
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:05,360
So cool. You're such
a professional!

77
00:05:05,450 --> 00:05:08,200
[XIAOYU LIN]
Mm. I grew up around them.

78
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:11,570
As long as I can remember,
I was raised by a sword spirit.

79
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:12,950
[camera clicks]

80
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:14,240
Where were your parents?

81
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,910
[GUO HAO, XIAOYU LIN]
Mm?

82
00:05:15,990 --> 00:05:19,530
I wish I could tell you.
They entrusted me to my sword.

83
00:05:19,610 --> 00:05:21,030
[GUO HAO]
So where is it now?

84
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:23,410
[XIAOYU LIN gasps]
Uh.

85
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:27,070
When I was eight years old,
she left and never returned.

86
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,490
The last thing she did
was leave me a note.

87
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:30,740
[XIAOYU LIN'S SWORD SISTER]
I'm headed to Songhai

88
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:33,110
for maintenance.
See you in a few days!

89
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:37,320
[SUN RONG gasps] You think she
ran into trouble or something?

90
00:05:37,410 --> 00:05:40,030
Who knows? I bet
she just got lost.

91
00:05:40,110 --> 00:05:43,030
She probably has a terrible
sense of direction like I do.

92
00:05:43,110 --> 00:05:45,200
[ALL]
Eh...

93
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,910
So, for all these years,

94
00:05:46,990 --> 00:05:49,450
I've worked in
different sword shops.

95
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:51,530
Hoping one day
I'll see her again.

96
00:05:51,610 --> 00:05:53,950
[CHEN CHAO whimpers]

97
00:05:54,030 --> 00:05:57,280
A beautiful tragedy. She refuses
to buy another sword

98
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:59,160
until she can see her
sword sister again.

99
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:02,200
Actually, no. I'm poor.

100
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,780
That's why.

101
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:04,990
[XIAOYU LIN giggles]

102
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,860
What about our sword class?

103
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:13,240
Wait, someone from your school
can't afford a sword?

104
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:16,110
That's surprising even
for Faction Sixty.

105
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,030
[LIANG ZHENG, LIANG FEI laugh]

106
00:06:18,110 --> 00:06:21,360
Ha! Great. Back for
revenge already?

107
00:06:21,450 --> 00:06:25,360
I wouldn't get too excited, kid.
Our swords need love, too.

108
00:06:25,450 --> 00:06:27,570
[LIANG ZHENG grunts]

109
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:31,070
Since she's good at her job,
I'll tip extra.

110
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,070
But I'm gonna need the whole
maintenance package,

111
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:36,700
sharpened and polished,
by tomorrow.

112
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:39,240
I would, sir, but this
is a large batch.

113
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:41,950
It'll take three days.

114
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:45,570
Excuse me. We already have her
booked for the rest of the day.

115
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:47,360
You'll need to find
someone else.

116
00:06:47,450 --> 00:06:50,160
[XIAOYU LIN]
Uh! No, no, no, no, no!

117
00:06:51,740 --> 00:06:54,660
It's fine. I'll stay
late and do both jobs.

118
00:06:54,740 --> 00:06:58,700
Ha! That's it.
You're a smart girl.

119
00:06:58,780 --> 00:07:01,160
Lin Xiaoyu, was it?

120
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:05,160
Just work hard and be better,
then you could get a bigger tip.

121
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,240
Maybe even afford that sword.

122
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:09,450
Don't patronize her!
I'll report you--

123
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,320
It's alright, Sun.

124
00:07:13,410 --> 00:07:15,160
I make my money per-job.

125
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:17,740
This gives me a
chance to earn more.

126
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,160
Are you sure?

127
00:07:21,110 --> 00:07:23,740
[TANG JINGZE laughs]

128
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:25,360
[TANG JINGZE]
Enjoy that paycheck,

129
00:07:25,450 --> 00:07:27,490
you're really gonna
earn it this week!

130
00:07:27,570 --> 00:07:29,200
[LIANG FEI]
Heh!

131
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:30,740
[CHEN CHAO]
Stupid Tang Birdie Two,

132
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:32,780
he's just a big bully.

133
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:36,200
She loves spiritual
swords so much,

134
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,860
but she doesn't even have one.

135
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:40,240
No wonder she's living
at the school.

136
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,740
Her life's pretty rough.

137
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:44,030
Would it be weird if
I just bought her one?

138
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:45,910
She wouldn't have
to work so hard.

139
00:07:45,990 --> 00:07:47,990
[GUO HAO]
Mm. I don't think you should.

140
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:49,660
Might hurt her self-esteem.

141
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:52,200
[CHEN CHAO] What if we did
a really cool fundraiser?

142
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,530
Huh? That's the same thing!

143
00:07:54,610 --> 00:07:55,910
[CHEN CHAO, GUO HAO]
Uh.

144
00:07:55,990 --> 00:07:57,990
This is where you
build your own.

145
00:07:58,070 --> 00:08:01,110
We could just...
forge one for her.

146
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:04,160
[CHEN CHAO] Wang Ling.
You're a genius, dude!

147
00:08:09,530 --> 00:08:10,740
[XIAOYU LIN grunts]

148
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:17,280
[XIAOYU LIN hums]

149
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:21,070
[GUO HAO] She was here so late.
When does the poor girl sleep?

150
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:24,200
Sun Rong, are you sure we won't
get in trouble for this?

151
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:26,780
It's fine. I got the
manager's permission.

152
00:08:26,860 --> 00:08:30,280
Works for me!
We got all the stuff?

153
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:33,910
Cool. Are you done
with the design?

154
00:08:33,990 --> 00:08:37,320
Not gonna lie, that's pretty
twisted, dude.

155
00:08:37,410 --> 00:08:41,570
What the hell, man? Let's go!
I'm so pumped, I can't take it!

156
00:08:41,660 --> 00:08:44,160
[SUN RONG gasps]
Hold on.

157
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:46,450
We need to analyze
our materials first.

158
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:48,360
We can't skip this step!

159
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:52,530
[GUO HAO grunts]

160
00:08:57,410 --> 00:08:58,910
[MALE ANNOUNCER A]
Spiritual beast bones.

161
00:08:58,990 --> 00:09:01,160
Three point five ounces.
Grade A.

162
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,660
[laughs]
I yanked these teeth out of

163
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:05,780
a level three night devil tiger.

164
00:09:05,860 --> 00:09:07,280
I pinned him down
with a sliding tackle.

165
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,200
Oh, come on, no one
likes a bragger.

166
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:12,030
[GUO HAO gasps]

167
00:09:12,110 --> 00:09:13,200
[MALE ANNOUNCER A]
Phecda meteorite.

168
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:15,860
Approximately Ten pounds.
Grade S.

169
00:09:15,950 --> 00:09:19,070
[GUO HAO gasps]
Where'd you find a Grade S item?

170
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,530
[CHEN CHAO chuckles]

171
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:27,360
[FATHER CHEN]
Hm. My Star of Fighters.

172
00:09:27,450 --> 00:09:31,280
May you bless the Chens
and our martial prowess.

173
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:36,610
[yells]

174
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:41,240
[CHEN CHAO chuckles]
Uh, from home.

175
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,660
Sun Rong! What stuff
did you bring?

176
00:09:47,450 --> 00:09:49,410
[MALE ANNOUNCER A]
Universal Hair Growth Lotion.

177
00:09:49,490 --> 00:09:50,910
Grade S-Plus Treasure.

178
00:09:50,990 --> 00:09:52,320
What is this thing?

179
00:09:52,410 --> 00:09:54,780
That kinda item is totally
out of our league!

180
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:56,910
[CHEN CHAO] Sun, where can
I find one of these?

181
00:09:56,990 --> 00:09:58,320
[GUO HAO gasps]

182
00:09:58,410 --> 00:10:01,030
[SUN RONG gigles] That's only
for us girls to know.

183
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,860
[CHEN CHAO, GUO HAO, SUN RONG]
What's that thing?

184
00:10:06,950 --> 00:10:08,160
I found it.

185
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,570
What's happening?

186
00:10:09,660 --> 00:10:11,820
The meter's going nuts,
I don't think it's gonna stop!

187
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:15,660
[GUO HAO gasping]
Why are you smacking it?

188
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:18,160
Stop it. You're gonna break it!

189
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:20,360
[GUO HAO yells]

190
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,160
[GUO HAO]
What does that mean?

191
00:10:27,410 --> 00:10:30,070
[CHEN CHAO chuckles] All right!
What do we do next?

192
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:33,280
According to this,
the next step is

193
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:36,240
taking all the materials and
smelting them in the furnace.

194
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,570
Right. How do we do that?

195
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,990
[GUO HAO]
We've come this far.

196
00:10:57,570 --> 00:10:59,110
[XIAOYU LIN]
Mm...

197
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,030
One, two...

198
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:11,860
[XIAOYU LIN]
Hm...

199
00:11:11,950 --> 00:11:14,410
[CHEN CHAO]
Yoo, hoo! Good morning!

200
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:19,030
You guys were faster than me!

201
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:20,610
Are you here to pick
up your swords?

202
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:22,450
[SUN RONG chuckles]

203
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:25,530
[SUN RONG]
For you.

204
00:11:25,610 --> 00:11:28,490
[CHEN CHAO] Heh. Spiritual sword
class starts soon.

205
00:11:28,570 --> 00:11:31,070
You didn't have one and
we didn't want you to get

206
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:34,360
left behind, so we thought...

207
00:11:34,450 --> 00:11:36,780
[GUO HAO] Maybe we could
combine some of our stuff

208
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:38,160
and make you one.

209
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,570
--[XIAOYU LIN whimpers]
--[CHEN CHAO, SUN RONG gasp]

210
00:11:43,070 --> 00:11:44,570
Is it no good?

211
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:47,410
We tried teaching ourselves in
the tutorial area. I'm sorry.

212
00:11:47,490 --> 00:11:51,570
I'm sorry, too. I didn't control
the temperature very well.

213
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:52,950
[CHEN CHAO]
No, it was my fault.

214
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:56,570
I was kinda nervous, so my
hammering was shaky.

215
00:11:56,660 --> 00:11:59,860
No, it's not that.
You did nothing wrong.

216
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:06,820
It just... looks so
much like my old one.

217
00:12:06,910 --> 00:12:09,610
[ALL gasp]

218
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:12,910
Wang Ling designed it.
He must have known!

219
00:12:12,990 --> 00:12:16,280
He's got such a gentle,
beautiful soul.

220
00:12:17,530 --> 00:12:19,780
You guys, thank you!

221
00:12:19,860 --> 00:12:23,110
This is the best gift ever,
and I love it!

222
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,160
It feels so great to
have a sword again!

223
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,740
[TANG JINGZE]
Congrats!

224
00:12:26,820 --> 00:12:29,990
You made a sword so ugly
she started crying!

225
00:12:30,070 --> 00:12:32,860
Ugh. You again?

226
00:12:32,950 --> 00:12:36,320
Why? Hasn't she done
enough for you?

227
00:12:36,410 --> 00:12:39,700
While you wasted your time
slacking off with friends,

228
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:41,660
I was having the store
manager take care of

229
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:43,200
the maintenance for me.

230
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:48,450
Ha! I'm sure it needed a lot of
work after I destroyed it.

231
00:12:48,530 --> 00:12:50,860
Isn't that right,
Tang Birdie Two?

232
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:54,450
[GUO HAO laughs]

233
00:12:54,530 --> 00:12:55,860
[CHEN CHAO grunts]

234
00:12:55,950 --> 00:12:57,160
[TANG JINGZE]
Tell me.

235
00:12:57,240 --> 00:13:00,070
She's one of your employees,
is she not?

236
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:04,700
Birdie-- Master Tang.

237
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:06,360
[TANG JINGZE]
As a VIP, aren't I allowed

238
00:13:06,450 --> 00:13:09,990
to ask any employee to
help test my blade?

239
00:13:10,070 --> 00:13:15,030
Excuse me. I'm a VIP too.
As such, I request her first.

240
00:13:15,110 --> 00:13:17,950
[MALE EMPLOYEE A]
Eh... Sorry, Miss Sun.

241
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:20,030
He has an appointment
before yours.

242
00:13:20,110 --> 00:13:21,200
